---
// Footer component - Enhanced with contact section
---

<footer id="contacto" class="bg-black scroll-mt-20">
  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <div class="bg-gnome-dark py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">CONTÁCTANOS</h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gnome-accent mx-auto mb-8"></div>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        ¿Quieres que toquemos en tu evento? ¿Tienes una propuesta de colaboración?
        <br />
        Escríbenos y nos pondremos en contacto contigo.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-black rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope text-gnome-accent text-3xl"></i>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Email</h3>
        </div>
        <a
          href="mailto:banda_blackgnome@gmail.com"
          class="text-xl text-gnome-accent hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors"
        >
          banda_blackgnome@gmail.com
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-black rounded-lg p-6">
          <i class="fas fa-music text-gnome-accent text-3xl mb-3"></i>
          <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Bookings</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Shows y presentaciones</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black rounded-lg p-6">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake text-gnome-accent text-3xl mb-3"></i>
          <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Colaboraciones</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Proyectos musicales</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-black rounded-lg p-6">
          <i class="fas fa-newspaper text-gnome-accent text-3xl mb-3"></i>
          <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Prensa</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Entrevistas y medios</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Social Media & Copyright -->
  <div class="py-12 px-4 border-t border-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Síguenos en redes sociales</h3>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/Black-Gnome-137521263728335/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-white hover:text-gnome-accent transition-all duration-300 text-4xl transform hover:scale-110"
            aria-label="Facebook"
          >
            <i class="fab fa-facebook-square"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/blackgnomeband/?hl=es-la"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-white hover:text-gnome-accent transition-all duration-300 text-4xl transform hover:scale-110"
            aria-label="Instagram"
          >
            <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBgsrdBzSi9i29rkm4nG1XQ/featured"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-white hover:text-gnome-accent transition-all duration-300 text-4xl transform hover:scale-110"
            aria-label="YouTube"
          >
            <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://soundcloud.com/user-36408607"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-white hover:text-gnome-accent transition-all duration-300 text-4xl transform hover:scale-110"
            aria-label="SoundCloud"
          >
            <i class="fab fa-soundcloud"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://vimeo.com/blackgnome"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-white hover:text-gnome-accent transition-all duration-300 text-4xl transform hover:scale-110"
            aria-label="Vimeo"
          >
            <i class="fab fa-vimeo-square"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copyright -->
      <div class="text-center pt-8 border-t border-gray-900">
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
          &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} BlackGnome. Todos los derechos reservados.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-2">
          Made with <span class="text-gnome-accent">♥</span> for metal lovers
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
